            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I also want to tack on that it may be useful in some cases to have a different `virt_text` for lines that are wrapped, when `virt_text_repeat_linebreak = true`. An additional `virt_text_wrapped` option that takes the same form as `virt_text` could be added for this?",
